					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You got problems with random data corruption/crashes on the spc?
<br />This is almost certainly caused by the echo buffer, as you already suggested.
<br />
<br />I believe I disabled echo in my music player because I didn't want to waste any precious RAM, but I did try it once.
<br />
<br />Absolutely make sure that you initialize the echo regs in the right order and with due delay between register writes! The latter is especially important.</div>

